last me until dinner!

59
00:07:15,417 --> 00:07:18,084
Huh? What's that noise?

60
00:07:24,084 --> 00:07:26,042
 Aaahhh!

61
00:07:26,584 --> 00:07:28,584
Yikes! Is he dead?!

62
00:07:29,917 --> 00:07:32,667
What the--?!

63
00:07:32,750 --> 00:07:34,250
