 Ow! Ooh!

77
00:08:11,417 --> 00:08:12,875
Uh. Hm?

78
00:08:16,209 --> 00:08:18,959
Holy cow! Whoa!
What was that?!

79
00:08:19,042 --> 00:08:22,125
But... How'd you...?
You shouldn't be alive, kid!

80
00:08:22,209 --> 00:08:24,584
 So you thought you
finished me off again, huh?!

