Alright monster!
It's your turn!

84
00:08:31,834 --> 00:08:34,334
Monster? Hold on!
I'm not a monster, kid!

85
00:08:34,417 --> 00:08:37,042
I'm a human being!
Just like you are!

86
00:08:37,125 --> 00:08:40,625
 You are?!
Uh, ugh... Really?!

87
00:08:40,709 --> 00:08:43,125
Yes! Uhh...

88
