93
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:53,584
A human you say?

94
00:08:53,667 --> 00:08:54,667
 That's right.
Wanna to see my

95
00:08:54,750 --> 00:08:57,167
certificate of authenticity?

96
00:08:57,250 --> 00:08:58,709
 No thanks.

97
00:09:00,917 --> 00:09:02,584
