as I possibly could.

111
00:09:29,500 --> 00:09:32,667
I see. Well!
What a nice thing to say!

112
00:09:32,750 --> 00:09:35,584
Your grandpa sounds like
a very wise man. Is he?

113
00:09:35,667 --> 00:09:39,084
