kid, you're really strong!

129
00:10:16,167 --> 00:10:18,959
Thanks! Grandpa trained
me to be like steel.

130
00:10:19,042 --> 00:10:21,292
Hey. You were driving
a car around, right?

131
00:10:21,375 --> 00:10:24,292
