 Wow!
That's a nice little place

171
00:12:04,459 --> 00:12:05,667
you've got there, kid!

172
00:12:05,750 --> 00:12:08,417
 Gee, thanks!
Just wait here one second.

173
00:12:10,209 --> 00:12:11,584
Huh?

174
00:12:14,542 --> 00:12:15,834
Listen.

175
00:12:15,917 --> 00:12:17,042
What's up?

176
